<h2>Hangman Word Games</h2>

Play Hangman word games in any language. Have fun while learning expressions, slang, proverbs, idioms and more.
Create Hangman word games to exchange language and culture. Discuss each game using it's message board.
It's a fun way to learn, make friends or find language exchange partners for regular practice!<br>
<br>
